<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.6">
<l>cōtta nampi yeṉṟutoṇṭar miṇṭitto ṭarntaḻaikku</l>
<l>mātta ṉampi ceṅkaṇampi yākiluntē varkkellām</l>
<l>mūtta nampi mukkaṇampi yeṉṟumuṉi varttoḻutu</l>
<l>ēttum nampi yemperumā ṉevvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The bright-eyed lord, the trusted lord to whom devotees call,</l>
<l>Following in throngs, saying, “Hail, lord!”</l>
<l>Our great lord, the lord whom sages praise and worship,</l>
<l>Saying, ‘Oldest lord of all the gods! Three-eyed lord,’</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who lies in Evvuḷ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
